"description":"Timehop is the only app that lets you celebrate all your best memories, every day. Join millions of people who start their day reminiscing with friends on a nostalgic journey. It's like #tbt every day!\n\n---\n\nWebby Awards Best Social App\n\nWebby Awards People’s Voice - Best Social App\n\nAs featured in The New York Times, Washington Post, Time Magazine, and Vox.\n\n---\n\nYour Daily Memories\n\n• See this exact day in history, every time you open\n• Tap or Swipe through every old photo, video, and post\n• Relive your favorite vacations, parties, and weddings\n• Go back 1 year ago, to 20 years ago, and beyond!\n\nAll Your Memories\n\n• Relive every photo you’ve taken, even the ones you never post\n• Catch every video a second time from your camera roll\n• Connect your Facebook, Google Photos, Dropbox, Flickr, Tumblr, and Swarm accounts to see your entire social history\n\nRelive the Best, Hide the Rest!\n\n• Cherish the best memories and protect yourself from the sad ones\n• Hide your bad memories so you don’t see them again next year\n• Go directly to the posts and delete them from where they were originally posted\n\nThen & Now\n\n• Compare the old with the new!\n• Snap a new selfie to show off just how much your hair has changed\n• Or grab a recent photo of your puppy to see how much they’ve grown\n\nReminisce with Friends\n\n• Share any memory easily with your friends via sms or other messaging platforms\n• Post your best throwbacks and share the memories with everyone\n• Crop, frame, and add stickers like a scrapbooking master\n\nYour Daily Habit\n\n• Every morning you get a new day of Timehop memories, and it only lasts for 24 hours!\n• Set alerts so you never miss a day\n• Your Timehop streak tracks how many days in a row you have checked your memories\n• Unlock badges and rewards the bigger your streak gets!\n\nNostalgic News\n\n• Watch Abe, our dinosaur mascot, report on the news of the past\n• Learn about the weird, lesser-known, and culturally significant historic moments\n• It’s a fun nostalgic fact every day\n\nRetroVideo\n\n• Don’t miss an episode of the best pop-culture nostalgia TV show\n• Catch clips of the movies, shows, and music memories on this day in a bitesize format\n• Impress your friends with just how much you remember from your childhood\n\n---\nSubscription Details:\n• Monthly and annual plans are available\n• Try Timehop+ with a 7-day free trial when you choose an annual plan\n• Payment will be charged to your Apple account\n• Your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period\n• Your subscription can be managed and the auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your settings in the App Store after purchase\n• Any unused portion of a free trial, if offered, will be forfeited when you purchase a subscription to that service\n\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.timehop.com/privacy\nTerms of Service: https://www.timehop.com/terms\n—\n\n\nWanna know more? Find us on Instagram and Facebook @Timehop, visit timehop.com, or contact us at help@timehop.com.\n\nHappy Timehopping!", "averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":4.8462399999999998811972545809112489223480224609375, "fileSizeBytes":"148843520", "formattedPrice":"Free", "userRatingCountForCurrentVersion":175074, "trackContentRating":"4+", "languageCodesISO2A":["EN", "ES"], "sellerUrl":"https://timehop.com", "averageUserRating":4.8462399999999998811972545809112489223480224609375, "trackCensoredName":"Timehop - Memories Then & Now", "trackViewUrl":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/timehop-memories-then-now/id569077959?uo=4", "contentAdvisoryRating":"4+", "minimumOsVersion":"16.6", "bundleId":"com.timehop.ios.Timehop", "genres":["Social Networking", "Photo & Video"], "userRatingCount":175074}, 
