"description":"A Walk Down Memory Lane\nYour favorite memories – one day at a time.\n\nEvery day, Memory Lane shows you the photos and videos you took on this day in years past.\nFrom quiet mornings to birthday parties, relive forgotten moments and the joy they carry.\n\nNo accounts. No tracking. No cloud. Just you and your story.\n\nYour memories stay yours.\nEverything is processed on your device. No data collection. No distractions.\n\nFeatures\n• Daily Flashbacks – See moments from this day in history\n• Sharing – Send memories to loved ones via the iOS Share Sheet\n• Favorites & Deletion – Keep only your favorites and minimize the rest (Pro)\n• Date Picker – Explore any date, not just today (Pro)\n• Fast & Offline – Works instantly, no internet needed\n• Widgets & Notifications – Subtle reminders, only if you want them\n\nFree Trial\nTry Memory Lane free for three days. If you love it, unlock Pro for a reduced price for a limited time.\n\nTerms of use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/", "averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":5, "fileSizeBytes":"56801280", "formattedPrice":"Free", "userRatingCountForCurrentVersion":12, "trackContentRating":"4+", "languageCodesISO2A":["EN"], "sellerUrl":"https://www.awesomepeoplesoftware.com/memorylane", "averageUserRating":5, "trackCensoredName":"Walk Down Memory Lane", "trackViewUrl":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/walk-down-memory-lane/id6743770625?uo=4", "contentAdvisoryRating":"4+", "minimumOsVersion":"15.1", "bundleId":"com.awesomepeoplesoftware.memorylane", "genres":["Photo & Video", "Lifestyle"], "userRatingCount":12}, 
