"description":"Join millions of parents who use the FREE Tinybeans app to privately capture and organize photos and videos of their kiddos and share them with loved ones—by invite only!\n\nTinybeans features:\n\n►PRIVATE PHOTO SHARING: Safely share every adorable baby photo and video with the family and friends you choose. Only your followers can view, react, and comment.\n\n►UPDATES FOR ALL: Invite all your kiddo’s biggest fans so everyone receives the same updates (no more time wasted sending each photo to seven group chats!).\n\n►PHOTO STORE: Pull photos and captions straight from your Tinybeans journal to create beautiful photo books and calendars right in your app.\n\n►MILESTONE TRACKER: Track more than 300 milestones to watch your baby grow and develop over time, from their first few weeks to age 6. It’s the perfect visual diary to browse whenever you’re feeling nostalgic.\n\n►EDIT PHOTOS: Have fun with photo sharing by adding text, stickers, filters, and effects. Find something for every moment with stickers for milestones, holidays, and more!\n\n►EASY TO USE: Not only is it simple to capture and organize your memories, but it couldn’t be easier for your loved ones to access updates via the app or email (perfect for grandparents!) and react and comment freely.\n\n►CALENDAR VIEW: Relive your favorite moments in our calendar view, where all your photos, videos, and milestones are conveniently organized by date.\n\n►CURATED SMART ALBUMS: If organizing your photos doesn’t spark joy, let us do it for you! We curate your memories by theme or date so you can share highlights from family trips, birthdays, or specific stretches of time with loved ones.\n\n►JOURNAL PROMPTS: We’ll ping you when it’s time to update a photo, but we’ll also inspire you to jot down a meaningful memory from time to time.\n\n►AUTOMATED RECAPS: Family and friends feel like they’re along for the ride thanks to our daily or weekly email updates recapping your little one’s sweetest moments and milestones.\n\nIf the idea of posting your kiddos on social media gives you an icky feeling, we get it! So we’ve made privacy a top priority, along with connecting families and capturing your everyday moments, big and small. A Tinybeans digital photo album is easy for parents to use and even easier for loved ones to engage with.\n\nTinybeans has been described as “a new mom’s best friend” and “ a grandparent’s treasured time capsule”. Millions of families agree: the next best thing to being there for every adventure is following along on Tinybeans.\n\n**Over 150,000 Five Star Reviews! Featured as App of the Day and seen in the New York Times, MSN, Parents, Fatherly, US Weekly, Forbes, and more!**\n\nAll plans let you upload, store, and share memories privately and securely with only the people you invite. But with Tinybeans+, you can create memories without limits, share larger files, and so much more! \n\nSubscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can turn off auto-renew at any time from your iTunes account settings.\n\nQuestions/feedback? Please reach out to us at info@tinybeans.com. We love to hear from you. Tinybeans website: https://tinybeans.com", "averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":4.86110000000000042064129956997931003570556640625, "fileSizeBytes":"328637440", "formattedPrice":"Free", "userRatingCountForCurrentVersion":104240, "trackContentRating":"4+", "languageCodesISO2A":["EN"], "sellerUrl":"http://www.tinybeans.com", "averageUserRating":4.86110000000000042064129956997931003570556640625, "trackCensoredName":"Tinybeans Private Family Album", "trackViewUrl":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/tinybeans-private-family-album/id521633042?uo=4", "contentAdvisoryRating":"4+", "minimumOsVersion":"15.0", "bundleId":"com.tinybeans.mobile.iphone", "genres":["Lifestyle", "Photo & Video"], "userRatingCount":104240}]
